---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<section
  class="nt-grain nt-grain-dark nt-hex-pattern"
  style="
    background: var(--nt-gradient-dark);
    padding: var(--nt-space-3xl) var(--nt-space-md);
    text-align: center;
  "
  aria-labelledby="cta-heading"
>
  <div
    style="
      max-width: 44rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    "
  >
    <p
      style="
        font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        color: var(--nt-color-green-400);
        margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-sm);
      "
    >
      Empieza aquí
    </p>

    <h2
      id="cta-heading"
      style="
        font-family: var(--nt-font-display);
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        color: var(--nt-color-stone-50);
        margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-lg);
      "
    >
      La primera consulta<br />
      <em style="font-style: italic; color: var(--nt-color-earth-400)">es gratuita.</em>
    </h2>

    <p
      style="
        font-family: var(--nt-font-body);
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        color: var(--nt-color-stone-300);
        margin-bottom: var(--nt-space-xl);
        max-width: 34rem;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
      "
    >
      Sin compromiso. Una conversación de 30–45 minutos para conocerte, entender tu situación y explicarte cómo trabajamos. Tú decides si seguimos.
    </p>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--nt-space-md); justify-content: center; align-items: center">
      <a
        href={`${base}/contacto`}
        style="
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          background: var(--nt-color-stone-50);
          color: var(--nt-color-green-900);
          font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
          font-weight: 600;
          font-size: 1rem;
          padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
          border-radius: 3px;
          text-decoration: none;
        "
      >
        Solicitar consulta gratuita
      </a>
      <a
        href={`${base}/servicios`}
        style="
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          color: var(--nt-color-stone-400);
          font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
          font-weight: 500;
          font-size: 0.9375rem;
          text-decoration: none;
        "
      >
        Ver servicios y tarifas →
      </a>
    </div>

    <p
      style="
        margin-top: var(--nt-space-lg);
        font-family: var(--nt-font-ui);
        font-size: 0.8125rem;
        color: var(--nt-color-stone-500);
      "
    >
      Consulta presencial en Asturias · Atención online para toda España
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
